text: Naomie Melanie Harris (born 6 September 1976) is a British movie, stage, voice, and television actress. She is known for her role as Tia Dalma/Calypso in Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Man's Chest and in Pirates of the Caribbean: At World's End. She was born in London on September 6, 1976 to a Jamaican mother and a Trinidadian father."Naomie Harris ." Yahoo! Movies, 2008. Harris played Winnie Mandela in the 2013 movie Mandela: Long Walk to Freedom.
